Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Santa Cruz Island
Description: This is one of the channel islands that is off the coast of Santa Barbara. It is home to the Island Fox, and it also has some great fishing spots. I always enjoy spending the day there.

Name: Jerusalem
Description: This is one of the oldest cities in the world.  It is rich in history and very religious.  I visited Jerusalm when I was 18 years old with my birthright group.

Name: Lake Cachuma
Description: A great place to spend the day and go camping also.  I really like going here because there is also a lot of interesting wildlife to see.

Name: Jackson Hole
Description: A beautiful place to visit.  This is my favorite place to go snowboarding.  Its also really cool to see all of the Elk.

Name: Niagra Falls
Description: Visited Niagra Fall last year when I stayed in Toronto.  The waterfall is one of the wonders of the world.
